{"tid":2037453,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"集思廣益 527 低成本表態方法","createTime":"2020-05-27T03:46:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-27T04:22:57.000Z","uid":255749,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"51b2ea3a78a7c01471e58121c21ee9811f5999e3","tid":2037453,"uid":255749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T03:46:45.000Z","msg":"現況係 <span style=\"color: gold;\">聚人</span>同<span style=\"color: gold;\">勇武</span><br />\n都<span style=\"color: gold;\">極高成本</span><br />\n重狗之下更加係有武力差距<br />\n<br />\n一係大量人一齊犧牲<br />\n而呢個其實時機未到<br />\n一係就用創意表態<br />\n<br />\n以前有連儂牆<br />\n而家呢？可以做返<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">1. 連儂牆/貼大字報<br />\n2. 塗鴉<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">3. 周街丟陰司紙感觸國殤</span><br />\n4. 去政府大樓瘋狂排隊<br />\n5. 食黃店</span><br />\n<br />\n拋磚引玉 認真用腦諗策略<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">咁多人每人丟一條街陰司紙成個香港白雪雪</span><br />\n如果有<span style=\"color: gold;\">黃黑</span>仲好<br />\n畫面都夠靚啦<br />\n<br />\n有無更多提議<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明明連燈係最有創意嘅地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c580089731371caa2fdad396843be7d23b6fead9","tid":2037453,"uid":255749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T03:47:14.000Z","msg":"自推 1"},{"pid":"803cf05b6b6cab339161ce5eac6baaa92cc36866","tid":2037453,"uid":255749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T03:47:30.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"7b24d5cf845451b45828bed7baa165d0eae9ca14","tid":2037453,"uid":255749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T03:47:44.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"605c46dbd3a53aa4aba639157388549c62e1c1f6","tid":2037453,"uid":151469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T03:48:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"583fd62e4290a6c3510b8df61a2c3c11e99aa917","tid":2037453,"uid":255749,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T03:48:31.00